            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, grind the <strong>walnuts</strong> in a <strong>pestle and mortar</strong> to form a smooth paste</p>\r\n<p>Tip: if you don't have a pestle and mortar, chop the walnuts very finely</p>\r\n<p>Peel and finely slice the <strong>shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>Dissolve&nbsp;1/2&nbsp;<span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>chicken stock cube</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
